    entry_requirements = '<div class="card-body program-tabs--card-body"> <div class="program-detail"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md"> <div audience="international" class="mb-3 d-none"> <h4>Entry requirements</h4> <p>For entry into most UniSC undergraduate degree programs, you need to have completed a minimum level of education similar to successful completion of Australian Year 12 with good grades.</p> <p>Further studies, for example, a semester or more at college or university, can also be considered for entry and may give you credit transfer towards a degree.</p> <p>Some examples of upper secondary qualifications and a guide to the minimum grades that UniSC will consider are listed <a data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="0" href="https://www.usc.edu.au/study/international-students/how-to-apply/step-2-check-entry-requirements/undergraduate-program-admission-requirements" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="https://www.usc.edu.au/study/international-students/how-to-apply/step-2-check-entry-requirements/undergraduate-program-admission-requirements">here</a>. These are minimum requirements and do not guarantee entry. Some programs may require higher grades. Alternative qualifications may also be considered on a case by case basis.</p> <p>If your qualification (grouped by country) is not listed, send the qualification transcripts with your application form to the <a data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="1" href="https://www.usc.edu.au/study/international-students/contact-the-international-office" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="https://www.usc.edu.au/study/international-students/contact-the-international-office">International Office</a> for assessment.</p> <h4>English language requirements</h4> <p>You will also need to meet the <a data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="2" href="https://www.usc.edu.au/study/how-to-apply/english-language-requirements" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="https://www.usc.edu.au/study/how-to-apply/english-language-requirement