usc.edu.au/study/how-to-apply/english-language-requirements" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="https://www.usc.edu.au/study/how-to-apply/english-language-requirements">English language requirements</a> for this program. If you do not meet the minimum requirements, you may be able to enrol in our <a href="/international/programs-and-fees/english-language-programs" title="English language programs">English Language Programs</a> to reach the required level for most of UniSC’s programs (exceptions apply to non-standard English requirement programs).</p> </div> <h4>Special selection criteria</h4> <p>Courses that involve field trips may require a degree of physical fitness and mobility.</p> <h4>Additional entry information</h4> <p>Applicants from a non-English speaking background must attain an IELTS (Academic) overall score of 6.0 with a minimum of 5.5 in each subtest.</p> </div> <div class="col-md"> <dl class="dl-columns dl-columns-even"> <dt> <span class="position-relative"> Recommended prior study <button class="btn btn-link summary-info-btn summary-info-btn--detail" data-target="#prereqsModal" data-toggle="modal"> <!-- <i class="fal fa-question-circle"></i> Font Awesome fontawesome.com --> </button> </span> </dt> <dd>English and at least one of the sciences</dd> </dl> </div> </div> <uib-accordion><div class="panel-group" ng-transclude="" role="tablist"> <div class="ng-scope ng-isolate-scope panel" id="program-iar" template-url="group-template.html" uib-accordion-group=""><div class="card-header"> <p class="mb-0" style="font-weight:bold;"> <button class="btn btn-link" ng-click="toggleOpen()" tabindex="0" uib-accordion-transclude="heading"> <span class="ng-binding" uib-accordion-header="">Inherent academic requirements</span> <!-- <i class="fal fa-chevron-down ml-auto"></i> Font Awesome fontawesome.com --> </button> </p> </div> <div aria-expanded="false" aria-hidden="true" class="collapse" style="height: 0px;" uib-collapse="!isOpen"> <div class="card-body" ng-transclude